s-global.website-files.com/636a6f81a287f5628189d717/637b83688c7bd8908bfb2101_Preapproved%20(big).svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="card-icon"/><div><h3 class="card-title">Tracking progress.</h3><div class="normal-text">We share quarterly internal hiring reports and our Diversity Officer conducts an audit of our People Team’s practices annually.</div></div></div></div><div class="w-layout-grid _2-column-4060-grid"><div id="w-node-_1cf62941-c642-57d3-1d9b-531425d036f3-4c045b28" class="card teal"><img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/636a6f81a287f5628189d717/637b836fcf7e15d492086ba2_Perks.svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="card-icon"/><div><h3 class="card-title">Building bonds.</h3><div class="normal-text">Our employee resource groups (ERGs) provide places for our team to find connections through shared experiences and form networks of support, community, and belonging.</div></div></div><div id="w-node-c34b37c7-fa4e-bbe5-b6f9-0a58fe6a104b-4c045b28" class="card blue"><img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/636a6f81a287f5628189d717/637b83684d6ce097dd98b3f1_Limits%20(big).svg" loading="lazy" alt="" class="card-icon"/><div><h3 class="card-title">Hiring equitably.</h3><div class="normal-text">We use a “structured interviewing” framework to ensure all candidates are evaluated equally throughout the interview process. We also encourage those whose experience doesn’t exactly match our job descriptions to apply — we’re always open to diverse perspectives.</div></div></div></div></div></div><div class="section black wf-section"><div class="container w-container"><div class="section-title center"><h2 class="heading-title white">Perks and benefits.</h2></div><div class="w-layout-grid _4-column-grid"><div id="w-node-a0669919-5aa0-5a91-78d8-09df6217c633-4c045b28" class="white-card _24-padding-all-around"><div class="green-cr _24px-bottm-margin"><img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/636a6f81a287f5628189d717/637b836820daa909371f805a_ic_suitcase.svg" loading="lazy" alt="dollar"/></div><h3 class="h3-card-title">Work wherever.</h3><div class="normal-text subtitle">Our offices are located in NYC, RVA, and remotely. We’re a distributed team with a tight-knit community.</div></div><div id="w-node-fb45bcd0-cffa-b38b-4abd-5bd8423fdf83-4c045b28" class="white-card _24-padding-all-around"><div class="yellow-cr _24px-bottom-margin"><img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/636a6f81a287f5628189d717/637b8368e3a0df32dd01e5a5_ic_ticket.svg" loading="lazy" alt="dollar"/></div><h3 class="h3-card-title">Team events.</h3><div class="normal-text subtitle">From our annual company Homecoming to team happy hours &amp; offsites, we like to have fun IRL and virtually.</div></div><div id="w-node-_6287e2c5-25f8-9a5a-a949-1922ad8ee550-4c045b28" class="white-card _24-padding-all-around"><div class="teal-cr _24px-bottom-margin"><img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/636a6f81a287f5628189d717/637b83685a48cfca7f76092e_ic_apple.svg" loading="lazy" alt="dollar"/></div><h3 class="h3-card-title">Learning &amp; development.</h3><div class="normal-text subtitle">Learning never stops. We host regular Lunch &amp; Learns, provide teams with individual education budgets, and organize peer learning communities for our managers.</div></div><div id="w-node-_97e2c885-2d41-60b3-f9c2-ccf3537b88ef-4c045b28" class="white-card _24-padding-all-around"><div class="blue-cr _24px-bottom-margin"><img src="https://assets-global.website-files.com/636a6f81a287f5628189d717/637b8368f4c1a3735f69e98b_ic_plane.svg" loading="lazy" alt="dollar"/></div><h3 class="h3-card-title">Unlimited PTO.</h3><div class="normal-text subtitle">Take the time off that you need. Really, we mean it. Employees also earn a 6-week paid sabbatical after 4 years with Petal.</div></div></div></div></div><div class="section gray hide-work wf-section"><div class="container w-container"><div class="section-title center"><h2 class="heading-title">Why we work at Petal.</h2></div><div class=